::The Cybertronian Fire::

The shots fired by Rampage, Inferno, and Tankorr hit the shields of the 
Cybertronian Fire, the mighty ship firing back.

Two laser batteries open fire on Rampage, two on Inferno, and two on Tankorr.

One of the missile launchers fires at Inferno, another at Tankorr.

The EMP cannons (paralize bots temporarily) fire at Tankorr, then settling 
down to recharge.
